description:
I was so happy to see a wonderful coffee shop in the Sunset.  It is always nice to find a quiet place to sit and talk with a friend without worrying about being overcrowded.

{What to get}
Iced Chai Tea Latte:  So delicious!  The taste was just right, both sweet and spicy. 
Eat it along with a madeleine cookie 

{Where to sit}
If the weather is nice and warm, enjoy sitting outside.  The tables are really neat!  Table top has coffee bean glued down. Check it out! :)

{Service & Ambiance}
Very friendly, fast, clean, simple and pretty organized

I will come back here again when I am hanging out in the Sunset. :D

Happy Yelping!
